    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-spec E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery through six individual throttle bodies, paired with a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanical upkeep is current, with the dual-VANOS system recently serviced and the rear subframe reinforced to handle the torque loads of the limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a factory-tuned suspension geometry that provides exceptional turn-in and high-speed stability. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its age, the drivetrain remains robust, making it an ideal candidate for an enthusiast seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 32500.0,
