    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW 540i in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic finish. This vehicle has been garage-kept and professionally detailed regularly, showcasing a deep luster in the paint with only very minor stone chips consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the Black Dakota leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, complemented by a smoke-free cabin and a pristine dashboard. All technological features, including the premium Harman Kardon sound system and the intuitive iDrive navigation, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is exceptional; it features a full service history with a recent synthetic oil change, a new battery, and a fresh set of Continental tires installed last season. The turbocharged inline-six engine runs smoothly, delivering the powerful yet refined performance this series is known for. This is a dependable, elegant sedan that is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without any hidden maintenance needs.",
      "price": 35800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
